<div id="pf30" class="pf w0 h44" data-page-no="30"><div class="pc pc30 w0 h44"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h45" alt="" src="bg30.png"/><div class="t m330 x1 h35 y714 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1844 </div><div class="t m3f7 x45 h35 y714 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1000 YEARS, Rev. 20 </div><div class="t m460 x42 h35 y714 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">New Earth </div><div class="t m261 xcf h35 y58d ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">First </div><div class="t m390 x3d h35 y715 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Resurrection </div><div class="t m20d x70 h35 y716 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Second </div><div class="t m52f xbc h35 y5ff ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Resurrection </div><div class="t m1e9 x1f h35 y717 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. What was Daniel shown would occur in heaven after a succession of </div><div class="t m472 x69 h35 y718 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">earthly powers had risen and fallen? What would happen at the </div><div class="t m4c5 x69 h35 y256 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">close of this heavenly event? Dan. 7:9, 10, 13, 14, 21, 22, 26, 27. </div><div class="t m257 xae h3b y719 ff4 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WED </div><div class="t m530 xae h34 y718 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NMI </div><div class="t m41e x9b h35 y71a ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Benefits loyal </div><div class="t m2a0 x76 h35 y639 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">universe </div><div class="t m185 x9a h35 y71b ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Investigative phase </div><div class="t m261 x97 h35 y584 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Book of Life) </div><div class="t m2fc x6d h35 y19d ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dan. 7, 8,12 </div><div class="t m531 x2 h35 y71c ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Removal of sin from </div><div class="t m20b x1a h35 y71d ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sanctuary </div><div class="t m354 xba h35 y71e ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">JUDGMENT </div><div class="t m295 x3e h35 y71a ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Benefits redeemed </div><div class="t m4ec x61 h35 y639 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review phase </div><div class="t m230 xba h35 y4ad ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rev. 20:4; </div><div class="t m427 x22 h35 y583 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 Cor. 6:1-3 </div><div class="t m195 x5 h35 y71f ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Scapegoat in </div><div class="t m2d3 xb h35 y71d ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wilderness </div><div class="t m1a2 x2a h35 y720 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Benefits forfeited </div><div class="t m510 x3c h35 y639 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Executive phase </div><div class="t m390 x7e h35 y71b ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 25:31-46 </div><div class="t m170 x80 h35 y583 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rev. 20:11-15 </div><div class="t m28f x86 h35 y71f ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Camp clean </div><div class="t m188 x2c h35 y721 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Second </div><div class="t m208 x2c h35 y722 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Advent </div><div class="t m45d xaf h35 y723 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Second </div><div class="t m1d9 x69 h35 y5ae ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Apartment </div><div class="t m261 xcf h35 y724 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">First </div><div class="t m390 x4e h35 y725 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Apartment </div><div class="t m2cc x27 h35 y490 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sanctuary Type </div><div class="t m260 x40 h35 y724 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ&apos;s Second Apartment </div><div class="t m258 xb6 h35 y725 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ministry of Judgment/Vindication </div><div class="t m3b6 x1f h34 y4a4 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heavenly court regarding the wicked. The full sweep of the final judgment </div><div class="t m4d6 x1f h34 y726 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was enfolded with the typical Day of Atonement just as an oak is enfolded </div><div class="t m301 x1f h34 y413 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">within an acorn. </div><div class="t m192 x69 h34 y727 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daniel chapter 7 portrays the convening of a great judgment in heaven </div><div class="t m1b7 x1c h34 y728 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">at some point after the 1260 year period of the little horn. Thus the judg-</div><div class="t m468 x1f h34 y729 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ment would begin after 1798. (See Dan. 7:25; Rev. 12:6, 14.) The </div><div class="t m2cf x1c h34 y2af ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophecies of Daniel 8:14 and 9:24-27 locate the beginning of this phase of </div><div class="t m4be x1c h34 y72a ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">judgment in 1844. Daniel 7:9, 10, 13, 14 direct attention particularly to the </div><div class="t mdd x1c h34 y72b ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beginning and the end of this pre-advent judgment. Christ receives His </div><div class="t m2f2 x1c h34 y72c ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eternal kingdom composed of the vindicated saints at the close of this </div><div class="t m213 x1c h34 y72d ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">judgment in heaven (Dan. 7:13, 14). The vision portrays an aspect of the </div><div class="t m467 x1c h34 y72e ff5 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">final </div><div class="t m1d1 xa9 h34 y72e ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">judgment that will take place </div><div class="t m171 x35 h34 y72f ff5 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">before Christ returns </div><div class="t m532 x78 h34 y72f ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the second time </div><div class="t m16a x1c h34 y730 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for His believing people. </div><div class="t m1a8 x1c h35 y435 ff1 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">48 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
